{"tid":1356250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有必要於各社區宣傳 光復香港 時代革命 理念","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:51:04.000Z","uid":27203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"930c0c50798c450decc259d3be0fde2b64657e74","tid":1356250,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:47:47.000Z","msg":"得連登仔嗌係冇意思<br />\n同埋班和理非好介意革命兩隻字<br />\n我地有必要正名做五大訴求運動既口號之餘<br />\n仲要草擬背後理念：「全面改革政府架構 落實真正雙普選」 <br />\n如果唔係只會比對家同和理非誤解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋解釋未來成立臨時立會既原意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：支持獨立 但係唔係而家 而家一定五大訴求行先"},{"pid":"549074a9f573909ae9ba7e460515f0542c907468","tid":1356250,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"應同請幫推"},{"pid":"9dd3dda41b9a9b9b93330f0ebb871224ee9fcac2","tid":1356250,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"而家好多淺黃都唔明想點"},{"pid":"8398cbd53291f2ddc847f04fbb39fc3eb0c1ce11","tid":1356250,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"92beeb56146dc06bb28e0a8caa40039eee89df26","tid":1356250,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"暫時最有效 一定靠連儂牆 同 蘋果立場宣傳"},{"pid":"64abb27a32e9cd372414418964367e66689f0891","tid":1356250,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:49:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03738dbe80e776ac8a070d9eae6816b928b51935","tid":1356250,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:49:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976cc6ce9f6ed957a870ec56566917157f2d6d00","tid":1356250,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-2